{"tid":198472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"多仔3:2摩納哥，拜仁1:1皇馬，馬體會0:0李城","createTime":"2017-04-12T14:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T02:54:12.000Z","uid":51951,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11efe5812484058f33ae5593816051a4b9b47fb6","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"琴晚炸彈事件，令到今晚有三場歐聯，維持原判估多蒙特3:2<br />\n估計拜仁先入一球，拉莫斯追和，次回合先生死相搏<br />\n馬體會同李城，鐵布衫對金鐘罩，應該全場壓住李城踢，但李城接馬體三百招不敗<br />\nin gakki we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/094751_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F094751_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=fcfbc2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i99y4gH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi99y4gH.gif&h=3186d5aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13ae7909bce65e31f9c385c24fb62387797ac8f2","tid":198472,"uid":17853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"dda597bf5e5d4f69cb92214c01758ba4c88788cc","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"終於輪到結衣出嚟估波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/113554_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F113554_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=398092f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42bedf23a8fd33e356cb1c11f7d3a6a7f5721de4","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十卜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cada36fa374a0f594e2e6ec9910b34365587c6","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"gakki都被人負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3og0IH7GMH4D1HZ0DC/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3og0IH7GMH4D1HZ0DC%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e97a6d66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bd9e8e2dd9c483559ee1d158f4a957920e96cf1","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"今晚歐聯主題曲：球王朗，氣魄更壯，球王朗，心中不必驚慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/115359_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F115359_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=5fba714a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d528563521f68ade3522d0a5f1339851c32c23ad","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-sjc2-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s750x750/sh0.08/e35/17495170_439599119714425_4067496151442522112_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sjc2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs750x750%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2F17495170_439599119714425_4067496151442522112_n.jpg&h=69dcd964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454d879f6faf0b3af657f39b0e70091155a50ec7","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-sjc2-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/e35/17881862_111554632729924_3089388362767794176_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sjc2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F17881862_111554632729924_3089388362767794176_n.jpg&h=c98d4584&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e03d752b71a8c1228ccf7182d81fef5caa752b78","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b55bf9447144ed2182e2e2e43dbe43554d93995","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"逼和皇馬振士氣 牀單軍團獵狐夠讓<br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)馬德里體育會自二月尾後各戰線未嘗一敗，上場西甲首都打吡更作客逼和皇家馬德里。主帥施蒙尼豪言今晚歐聯八強首回合，乘李斯特城客戰一向防守甩漏甚多延續強勢，今仗可直取讓球主客和讓一球「主勝」。<br />\n<br />\n 自二月尾西甲主場1:2不敵巴塞隆拿後，牀單軍團之後各賽事八場五勝三和不敗，期間只失三球，上仗馬德里打吡更憑射手基沙文末段建功，作客1:1在宿敵皇馬身上搶回一分。全軍上下士氣正旺，施蒙尼揚言要保持這團火︰「己隊不止基沙文一人值得讚賞，每名球員在陣中都表現出不願落敗的決心，希望大家在今晚歐聯亦要展示出這顆鬥心。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然李斯特城的英超封王神話不再，目前只排第十一位還未解除降班威脅，但施蒙尼提醒戰將道︰「狐狸是一個陌生的對手，故今仗亦不易應付。」幸而，馬體會過去歐戰主場迎戰英格蘭球會五勝五和不敗，而且近九場歐戰作東亦取得七勝兩和佳績，給予球迷更大信心。<br />\n 李斯特城周日英超半力出擊，作客2:4不敵愛華頓，各戰線六連勝走勢終結，領隊沙士比亞解釋︰「我必須讓主力有足夠休息，確保他們能以最佳狀態迎接今晚關鍵一戰。」上仗沒有列入大軍名單的守將丹尼森遜、基斯甸富治斯和後備上陣的中場馬列斯預計都會重返正選。不過，狐狸作客成績慘不忍睹，各賽事近六場僅一勝五負共失十二球，隊長兼中堅韋斯摩根今晚又因傷缺陣，防線雪上加霜，故「主勝」可取。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5aa04g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5aa04g.gif&h=cde95933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02dc6b7a478511d3303a769eb92e4cf669b611df","tid":198472,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩拉結衣落水"},{"pid":"1b07038ba035f1add47b9a1c30249d889ec3c19a","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩拉結衣落水</blockquote><br />\n你個名太可愛，會帶來好運。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958c19f22383008395cd4f9216523a43b308f2bb","tid":198472,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"31a0af872dca7b9ef46151a674c1c8d0be80afe0","tid":198472,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"呢三個波膽三串一有幾多倍"},{"pid":"7a0cb1a54fe37e1892018387b28ae5de8b63ed28","tid":198472,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"試跟"},{"pid":"8abae75996e68d5675da8d0d7e04acfdf3a6cd78","tid":198472,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢三個波膽三串一有幾多倍</blockquote><br />\n825"},{"pid":"52b30e9c083040d8077e31361977a9c1249bc5ba","tid":198472,"uid":56360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"見到呢個po 係綠份 gun"},{"pid":"cfd8358f111f868d7fd47309728855009386bc06","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十卜</blockquote><br />\n多謝清連續兩晚支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295ba88470e442e52e684f9fc2394aa8a2eef7b0","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢三個波膽三串一有幾多倍</blockquote><br />\n825</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ecad8d91b7015073aa55d72a9067d9febb38a1","tid":198472,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到呢個po 係綠份 gun</blockquote><br />\n同gakki有緣分，但隨心估唔好跟"},{"pid":"6c4ec68f29b88b3c9e38946085d3dbbd2906c1a1","tid":198472,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":